* {{ill|Kuninotokotachi no Mikoto|ja|еӣҪеёёз«Ӣе‘Ҫ|1=Kuni-no-Tokotachi|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuninotokotachi no Mikoto|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuni-no-Tokotachi|qq=}}

