* {{ill|Ikutama-no-Mikoto|ja|еӨ©жҙ»зҺүе‘Ҫ|1=Ame-no-Ikutama|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ikutama-no-Mikoto|13=User:Immanuelle/Ame-no-Ikutama|qq=}} (Ikutama-no-Mikoto)
* {{ill|Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto|lt=Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto|lt=Kotoshironushi|ja|дәӢд»Јдё»е‘Ҫ|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kotoshironushi|qq=}} (Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto)
* {{ill|Mizuhanome|ja|ејҘйғҪжіўиғҪеЈІзҘһ|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizuhanome|qq=}} (Mizuhanome-no-Mikoto)

