* {{ill|Sukunabikona|ja|е°‘еҪҰеҗҚе‘Ҫ|1=Sukunabikona|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sukunabikona|13=User:Immanuelle/Sukunabikona|qq=}} (Sukunabikona-no-Mikoto)
