* {{ill|Kuninotokotachi|ja|еӣҪеёёз«Ӣе‘Ҫ|1=Kuni-no-Tokotachi|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuninotokotachi|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuni-no-Tokotachi|qq=}} (Kuninotokotachi-no-Mikoto)

== Auxiliary Shrines ==
* '''HЕҚri Shrine''' (зҘқзҘһзӨҫ)
''' Enshrines {{ill|Takehirokunioshihitohinomikoto|ja|жӯҰдә”зҷҫе»әе‘Ҫ|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takehirokunioshihitohinomikoto|qq=}} (a {{ill|Kuni no miyatsuko|ja|еӣҪйҖ |qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuni no miyatsuko|qq=}} of {{ill|Shinano Province|ja|з§‘йҮҺеӣҪ|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinano Province|qq=}} and associated with the {{ill|Mori ShЕҚgunzuka Kofun|ja|жЈ®е°Ҷи»ҚеЎҡеҸӨеўі|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mori ShЕҚgunzuka Kofun|qq=}}), {{ill|Takeminakata|ja|е»әеҫЎеҗҚж–№еҜҢе‘Ҫ|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeminakata|qq=}} (ancient name of the {{ill|Suwa Taisha|ja|и«ҸиЁӘеӨ§зӨҫ|1=Suwa-taisha|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suwa Taisha|13=User:Immanuelle/Suwa-taisha|qq=}} upper shrine deity), and {{ill|Minakatatomi|ja|еҚ—ж–№еҲҖзҫҺе‘Ҫ|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minakatatomi|qq=}} (ancient name of the lower shrine deity).

